sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as History or Changes Webview
participant Router as Feature Message Router
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as ConflictedActionUseCase
participant Worktree as Worktree

User->>App: Cherry-pick or revert commit
App->>Router: action request(worktreeLocator, commit)
Router->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Worktree
Router->>UseCase: execute action
alt Cherry-pick selected
  UseCase->>Worktree: cherryPick(commit, options)
else Revert selected
  UseCase->>Worktree: revertCommit(commit, options)
end
alt Git reports conflicts
  UseCase->>Worktree: getStatus()
  UseCase-->>Router: conflict state
  Router-->>App: conflict push with paths
  User->>App: Resolve files and continue
  App->>Router: continue request(worktreeLocator, actionKind)
  Router->>UseCase: continue action
  alt Continue cherry-pick
    UseCase->>Worktree: continueCherryPick()
  else Continue revert
    UseCase->>Worktree: continueRevert()
  end
  Router-->>App: operation success and refresh requested
else User aborts
  App->>Router: abort request(worktreeLocator, actionKind)
  alt Abort cherry-pick
    Router->>Worktree: abortCherryPick()
  else Abort revert
    Router->>Worktree: abortRevert()
  end
  Router-->>App: operation aborted and refresh requested
end
